## Why This Is Asked

Tests ability to design cryptographic isolation and operational controls for multi-tenant data in GCP. Assesses understanding of CMKs, envelope encryption, and how to integrate rotation, access policies, and automated validation into CI/CD to prevent data leakage and enable safe rollback.

## Key Concepts

- Customer-managed keys (CMKs) in Cloud KMS
- Envelope encryption for DB and object storage
